    "Therefore, we can see a number of influential deep learning techniques for code stemming from the area of code generation.",
    "Table 4 highlights the main technical contributions in code generation.",
    "Since code completion is one of the most important code generation applications, we also survey deep learning-based code completion.The primary contributions of the analyzed studies can be classified into nine distinct categories, highlighting the diverse range of advancements and innovations within code generation.",
    "Enhancing code structure informationSix studies highlight the oversight of rich structural information in many code generators [106].",
    "To address this concern, diverse approaches have been proposed for incorporating additional code structure information into their DL-based models, aiming to enhance the overall performance."
